---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Linux Directory">
  <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px;">
    
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 50px;">
      <h1 style="font-size: 3rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #1a202c;">About Linux Directory</h1>
      <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: #4a5568;">
        Curating the best open-source tools for the Linux community
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div style="background: white; border-radius: 20px; padding: 40px; border: 2px solid #e2e8f0; margin-bottom: 40px;">
      
      <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #1a202c;">Our Mission</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #4a5568; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 30px;">
        Linux Directory exists to help developers, system administrators, and Linux enthusiasts discover the best open-source tools and software. We believe in the power of community-driven curation to surface high-quality tools that might otherwise go unnoticed.
      </p>
      
      <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #1a202c;">Why We Built This</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #4a5568; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 30px;">
        The Linux ecosystem is incredibly rich, but finding the right tools can be overwhelming. We created this directory to provide a curated, community-driven resource where you can:
      </p>
      
      <ul style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #4a5568; line-height: 1.7; margin-left: 30px; margin-bottom: 30px;">
        <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Discover tools organized by category and use case</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Find detailed descriptions and links to official resources</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">See pricing models and licensing information</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Submit your own favorite tools to help others</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #1a202c;">Community-Driven</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #4a5568; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 30px;">
        Every tool in our directory is submitted and reviewed by the community. We believe the best recommendations come from real users who have experience with these tools in production environments.
      </p>
      
      <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #1a202c;">Get Involved</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #4a5568; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        Help us grow this resource:
      </p>
      
      <div style="display: flex; gap: 15px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <a href="/submit" style="background: #2563eb; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">
          Submit a Tool
        </a>
        <a href="mailto:hello@thelinuxforum.com" style="border: 2px solid #2563eb; color: #2563eb; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">
          Contact Us
        </a>
      </div>
      
    </div>
    
  </div>
</Layout>